<http://guia-mad-bench.es/data/course-guide/anx-pr-cl-001-01> a guide:CourseGuide ;
    sch:name "53001642 - Smart Grids"@en ;
    dct:title "ANX-PR/CL/001-01 GUÍA DE APRENDIZAJE"@es ;
    guide:numberOfCredits 3^^xsd:decimal ;
    guide:syllabusDescription "In this course, the fundamentals of smart grids are covered. In particular, attention is paid to intelligent micro and nano electric power grids..."@en ;
    sch:description "Guía de Aprendizaje para la asignatura Smart Grids en el Doble Master Universitario Ingenieria Industrial - Electronica Industrial"@es .

